== 歷史 ==
[[File:Courtney_Park_and_410.JPG|thumb]]
隨著[[賓頓|賓頓]]於1960年代末急速發展，當局亦於同期展開410號公路的規劃工序。安省公路部於1965年5月25日公佈《多倫多地區西部公路規劃研究報告》，提出在[[皮爾區|皮爾區]]和[[荷頓區|荷頓區]]建設數條新公路及將數條固有公路擴濶，當中包括10號公路<ref>{{cite news

 | title    = 700 Million Freeways West of Metro
 | work     = Globe and Mail
 | location = Toronto
 | date     = May 26, 1966
 | volume   = 123
 | issue    = 36,335
 | section  = News
 | pages    = 1, 25}}</ref>。然而，該研究報告沒有提及賓頓鎮議會倡議興建的貨車繞道。時任賓頓鎮長布賴頓（{{lang|en|William H. Brydon}}）於1969年向公路部提出將心湖道（{{lang|en|Heart Lake Road}}）走線改建成該貨車繞道，並將之往南伸延至401號公路<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Brampton Groups Ask for Pedestrian Mall
 | work       = The Toronto Star
 | date       = July 2, 1969
 | section    = Peel/Halton
 | page       = 41}}</ref><ref name="BramptonExpressway">{{cite news

 | title      = Expressway to Link Brampton with 401 Mayor Tells Council
 | work       = The Toronto Star
 | date       = December 30, 1969
 | section    = Peel/Halton
 | page       = 31}}</ref>；而布賴頓的繼任人阿治迪勤（{{lang|en|Jim Archdekin}}）則於翌年宣佈與公路部長戈姆（{{lang|en|George Gomme}}）商討繞道的走線<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Brampton Plans Discussion with McKeough
 | work       = The Toronto Star
 | date       = January 15, 1970
 | section    = Peel/Halton
 | page       = 63}}</ref>。公路部在往後數月就此進行研究，並於8月發表報告<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Bypass Report Due in Brampton
 | work       = The Toronto Star
 | date       = August 28, 1970
 | section    = Peel/Halton
 | page       = 31}}</ref>。

來自賓頓的戴維斯（{{lang|en|Bill Davis}}）就任[[安大略省省長|安大略省省長]]後，正式啓動沿心湖道走廊興建410號公路的項目<ref name="teh">{{cite report
 |title        = The History of Toronto's Unfinished Expressway System
 |publisher    = Energy Probe<!-- Note: Strikingly familiar to the former Get Toronto Moving Tranportation plan. -->
 |date         = April 5, 2009
 |url          = http://ep.probeinternational.org/2009/04/05/history-torontos-unfinished-expressway-system/
 |accessdate   = January 23, 2012
 |archive-date = 2020-09-19
 |archive-url  = https://web.archive.org/web/20200919092827/https://ep.probeinternational.org/2009/04/05/history-torontos-unfinished-expressway-system/
 |dead-url     = no
}}</ref>。介乎10號公路（曉倫大略街）和[[安大略427號省道|427號公路]]之間的一段401號公路於1975年起從來回六線行車擴濶至八線，而當局亦於同期加設連接心湖道和401號公路的交流道<ref>{{cite news

 | title      = Years of Headaches Driver' Prospect as 401 is Widened
 | first      = Thomas
 | last       = Claridge
 | work       = The Globe and Mail
 | location   = Toronto
 | date       = May 3, 1975
 | volume     = 132
 | issue      = 39,125
 | page       = 1}}</ref>。心湖道在往後年間改建成與其他道路立交的公路，介乎401號公路和賓頓女王街的路段於1978年11月15日開通，並同時正式編號為410號公路<ref name="opened1978">{{cite press release

 | title     = Highway 410 Opens November 15
 | author    = Public and Safety Information Section
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | date      = November 9, 1978}}</ref><ref>{{cite report

 | title     = Annual Report
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | date      = March 31, 1979
 | section   = Regional and District Operations: Central Region
 | page      = 14}}</ref><ref>{{cite map

 | title       = Ontario Road Map
 | cartography = Cartography Section
 | publisher   = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year        = 1980–81
 | inset       = South-Central Ontario}}</ref>，但來回方向合共只得兩條行車線。

當局其後動工擴濶410號公路，先在1983年完成跨越怡陶碧谷溪（{{lang|en|Etobicoke Creek}}）東支流的溝道<ref>{{cite web
 |title       = Etobicoke and Mimico Creeks Watershed
 |publisher   = Toronto Region Conservation Authority
 |url         = http://trca.on.ca/the-living-city/watersheds/etobicoke-mimico-creek/
 |accessdate  = February 20, 2012
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20120316085905/http://trca.on.ca/the-living-city/watersheds/etobicoke-mimico-creek/
 |archivedate = 2012年3月16日
}}</ref>和克拉克大道的交匯處<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1983–1984<!-- April 1983 -->
 | page      = XII
 | isbn      = }}</ref>，再於翌年批出合約興建跨越奧倫達道（{{lang|en|Orenda Road}}）以南[[加拿大國家鐵路|加拿大國家鐵路]]軌道的來回方向行車橋<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1984–1985<!-- April 1984 -->
 | page      = XII
 | isbn      = }}</ref>以及女王街交匯處，分別於1984年末和1985年末完成。波維爾德徑交匯處亦於1985年動工，1986年夏季完成<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1986–1987<!-- April 1986 -->
 | page      = XII
 | isbn      = }}</ref>。到了1988年，介乎士刁士大道和波維爾德徑的路段來回合共兩條行車線開通<ref name="1988r">{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1988–1989<!-- April 1988 -->
 | page      = XIII
 | isbn      = }}</ref>。

當局從1987年起將未來407號公路以南的路段從來回兩線行車擴濶至六線，同時動工興建士刁士大道以北的410號公路南行線<ref name="1988r" /><ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1989–1990<!-- May 1989 -->
 | page      = 10
 | isbn      = }}</ref>，到1990年則動工興建歌特尼公園徑交匯處。到1991年中，介乎401號公路和波維爾德徑的410號公路已告完成<ref>{{cite book

 | title     = Provincial Highways Construction Projects
 | author    = Transportation Capital Branch
 | publisher = Ministry of Transportation and Communications
 | year      = 1991–1992<!-- May 1991 -->
 | page      = 9
 | isbn      = }}</ref>。此外，當局在改建401號公路成長途線和短途線分隔行車安排（{{lang|en|collector-express system}}）的同時亦改建401號和410號公路的交匯處；該交匯處首條交流道於1990年8月28日開通，餘下的交流道則於同年年終前分階段通車<ref>{{cite news

 | title     = Police Fear New Ramps Will Worsen 401 Tie-ups
 | first     = Peter
 | last      = Howell
 | work      = Toronto Star
 | date      = August 28, 1990
 | section   = News
 | page      = A2}}</ref>。該交匯處連接403號和410號公路的交流道則於1991年秋季動工<ref>{{cite news

 | title   = Work Starts on 403-410 Link
 | first   = Bob
 | last    = Mitchell
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = December 5, 1991
 | section = Mississauga 
 | page    = MA2}}</ref>，1992年11月2日開通，耗資730萬元興建<ref>{{cite news

 | title   = 403-410 Highway Link Ready, Seen As 'Boon' To Motorists
 | first   = Bob
 | last    = Mitchell
 | work    = The Toronto Star
 | date    = October 31, 1992
 | section = News
 | page    = A24}}</ref>。

